               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; name of the donors; incipits of sections/miracles; word "sälam" in Text III; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
On the incipit page of Texts I, II and III (fols. 3r, 62r, 78r), a few lines are rubricated alternating with black lines.</rubric>
